    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>SEED SETBACK FOR MONSANTO</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Jennifer L. Rich</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Rich, Jennifer L</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Brazilian court upholds injunction blocking Monsanto from selling genetically modified soybeans in country until comprehensive environmental impact study is completed (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Regional Federal Court in Brazil upheld an injunction that blocks Monsanto from selling genetically modified soybeans in the country until a comprehensive environmental impact study can be completed. The initial injunction was handed down in 1998 in response to legal action brought by the Brazilian Consumer Defense Institute in alliance with Greenpeace. Monsanto can appeal the decision to the Supreme Tribunal of Justice, Brazil's Supreme Court.</p>
        <p>Jennifer L. Rich</p>
      </block>
